dct_description_sm: Abstract: Digital scan of a physical map of Africa from a late-19th century Russian encyclopedia.
Notes: Relief shown by gradient tints and hachures. Depths shown by isolines.
From: En͡tsiklopedicheskiĭ slovarʹ / pod redak͡tsiei professora I. F. Andreevskago. Tom I-XLIA ... Izdateli: F. A. Brokgauz (Leĭp͡tsig) I. A. Efron (S.-Peterburg). S.-Peterburg, 1890-1904.
